Class ComplexNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.zemris.java.tecaj.hw2.ComplexNumber

  • public class ComplexNumber
extends java.lang.Object
    Complex number class that allows manipulation on imaginary numbers. ComplexNumber represents an unmodifiable complex number.
